 <span data-ttu-id="f1bfd-670">若要提供使用者語彙基元，使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RequestRecognizerUpdate%2A>或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RequestRecognizerUpdate%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1bfd-670">To provide a user token, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RequestRecognizerUpdate%2A> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RequestRecognizerUpdate%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1bfd-671">若要指定的音訊位置的位移，請使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RequestRecognizerUpdate%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1bfd-671">To specify an audio position offset, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RequestRecognizerUpdate%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
